paragraphs.title: Create Phoenix Table (Season Data)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS mm_season (
    id VARCHAR, 
    season VARCHAR, 
    day VARCHAR, 
    wteam VARCHAR, 
    wscore INTEGER, 
    lteam VARCHAR, 
    lscore INTEGER, 
    wloc VARCHAR, 
    ot VARCHAR
    CONSTRAINT mypk PRIMARY KEY (id))
    SALT_BUCKETS = 1

paragraphs.title: Create Phoenix Table (Team Data)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS mm_teams (
    team_id VARCHAR, 
    team_name VARCHAR
    CONSTRAINT mypk PRIMARY KEY (team_id))
    SALT_BUCKETS = 1

paragraphs.title: Phoenix Joins & Aggregations: Top 15 Teams with the most Wins
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)

SELECT WTEAM_NAME, COUNT(*) AS WINS 

    FROM 

    (
    SELECT mm_season.*, 
        teams2a.team_name AS WTEAM_NAME, 
        teams2b.team_name AS LTEAM_NAME
        FROM mm_season
        LEFT JOIN mm_teams teams2a ON (mm_season.wteam = teams2a.team_id)
        LEFT JOIN mm_teams teams2b ON (mm_season.lteam = teams2b.team_id) 
    ) 
    
    GROUP BY WTEAM_NAME 
    ORDER BY WINS DESC 
    LIMIT 10

paragraphs.title: Phoenix Joins & Aggregations: Top 15 Teams with the most Losses
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)

SELECT LTEAM_NAME, COUNT(*) AS LOSSES 

    FROM 

    (
    SELECT mm_season.*, 
        teams2a.team_name AS WTEAM_NAME, 
        teams2b.team_name AS LTEAM_NAME
        FROM mm_season
        LEFT JOIN mm_teams teams2a ON (mm_season.wteam = teams2a.team_id)
        LEFT JOIN mm_teams teams2b ON (mm_season.lteam = teams2b.team_id) 
    ) 
    
    GROUP BY LTEAM_NAME 
    ORDER BY LOSSES DESC 
    LIMIT 10

paragraphs.title: Calculate the Top 15 Matchups with the biggest score difference
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)

SELECT SEASON, WSCORE, LSCORE, WLOC, (WSCORE-LSCORE) AS SCORE_DIFF, WTEAM_NAME, LTEAM_NAME

    FROM 

    (
    SELECT mm_season.*, 
        teams2a.team_name AS WTEAM_NAME, 
        teams2b.team_name AS LTEAM_NAME
        FROM mm_season
        LEFT JOIN mm_teams teams2a ON (mm_season.wteam = teams2a.team_id)
        LEFT JOIN mm_teams teams2b ON (mm_season.lteam = teams2b.team_id) 
    ) 
    
    ORDER BY SCORE_DIFF DESC
    LIMIT 1000
